TY  - JOUR
T1  - An Implicit Enumeration Algorithm for Quadratic Integer Programming
AU  - McBride, R. D.
AU  - Yormark, J. S.
Y1  - 1980/03/01
PY  - 1980
DA  - 1980/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.26.3.282
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.26.3.282
T2  - Management Science
JF  - Management Science
JO  - Management Science
SP  - 282
EP  - 296
VL  - 26
IS  - 3
PB  - INFORMS
N2  - We present an implicit enumeration algorithm for a nonseparable quadratic integer programming problem. We utilize fathoming criteria derived from Lemke's complementary pivot algorithm, and compare the use of pseudo-costs versus generalized penalties as a guide to branching. Computational experience is provided.
AB  - We present an implicit enumeration algorithm for a nonseparable quadratic integer programming problem. We utilize fathoming criteria derived from Lemke's complementary pivot algorithm, and compare the use of pseudo-costs versus generalized penalties as a guide to branching. Computational experience is provided.
